    "long_instructions": "## Video Game Developer - Providing a Single Example\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a video game developer by adding a single example to help guide the AI's dialogue.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI to generate a conversation by including **a brief example** of a hero-villain exchange.\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, noticing how the AI uses the example to shape tone, style, or plot.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Write a dialogue between a hero and villain where the villain reveals their ultimate plan. For example:\r\n>\r\n> Hero: \"You can't stop me.\" \r\n>\r\n> Villain: \"We'll see about that. I've just slashed the tires of your car so you won't be able to get to the courtroom in time!\" \r\n:::\r\n\r\n## Video Game Developer - Providing Multiple Examples\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a video game developer by guiding the AI with clear structure and multiple expectations for the dialogue.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI to generate a conversation by including **multiple examples** of a hero-villain exchange.\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the added structure affects the story flow, character depth, and tension.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Write a dialogue between a hero and villain. For example:\r\n>\r\n> Hero: \"You can't stop me.\" \r\n>\r\n> Villain: \"We'll see about that. I've just slashed the tires of your car so you won't be able to get to the courtroom in time!\" \r\n>\r\n> OR\r\n> \r\n> Batman: [in the interrogation room] \"Then why do you want to kill me?\"\r\n> \r\n> Joker: [giggling] I don’t, I don’t want to kill you! What would I do without you? Go back to ripping off mob dealers? No, no, NO! No. You... you... complete me.\"\r\n>\r\n> OR\r\n> \r\n> SKYFIRE: \"No, Ash. You still have a choice. You always did. Come back with me — let’s fix this. Together.\"\r\n>\r\n> SHADOWSTRIKE (softens, but masks it): \"You’re too late, Skyfire. The damage is already done.\"\r\n:::",
